    "description": "FLIGHT SOLUTIONS Inc. engages in the SI, payment, and EC businesses in Japan. The company offers Payment Meister and Incredist Premium II, which are applications and payment terminals that enable payments via tablet; Taipon, a touch payment solution for Android devices; payment solutions for unmanned automated payment machines and personal computers; and myVerifist, a solution for identity verification using number cards. It also provides IT services, such as IT and system consulting, system operation, support for system development using cloud services, and design and development support; Scenaria for Pepper and Sota; Elite Stalion; and cloud integration and robot solutions. In addition, the company offers EC-Rider B2BJ Series, a B2B EC site construction package, as well as consulting services related to package implementation, and system development and maintenance services. It serves logistics and finance companies. The company was formerly known as Flight System Consulting Inc. and changed its name to FLIGHT SOLUTIONS Inc. in June 2013. FLIGHT SOLUTIONS Inc. was incorporated in 1988 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
